  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK170">
<l>aḻukkaṟ ṟakaṉṟāru millaiyaḵ tillār</l>
<l>perukkattiṟ ṟīrntāru mil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Never have the envious become great never have those who are free from envy been without greatness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
